General.Name: Alliance Aviation Services Ltd
General.Description: Alliance Aviation Services Limited provides contract, charter, and allied aviation services in Australia and internationally. The company offers specialized aviation services, including aircraft wet leasing, dry leasing, airport management, aircraft trading, parts sales, engine leasing, and engineering services for airlines and clients. It operates a fleet of 100 seat aircraft F100; 80 seat aircraft F70; and 1 Embraer aircraft. The company serves mining, energy, tourism, and government sectors, as well as corporates, and educational and sporting customers. Alliance Aviation Services Limited was founded in 2002 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
